<!--
  Not used as a Rails-style "yield" layout — this project has no
  express-ejs-layouts dependency, so EJS has no built-in mechanism for a
  view to inject itself into a shared wrapper. Kept here only as a copy of
  the header/footer markup for reference; actual views under `auth/`
  include `partials/header` and `partials/footer` directly, the same
  pattern v1 uses (see v1-inseguro/src/views/partials/header.ejs).

  CSP note: helmet restricts scriptSrc to 'self' (see
  src/config/helmet.js) — do not add the Lucide CDN <script> tag v1 uses in
  its footer, it will be blocked. Icons are skipped for the auth module.
-->
